OL,3,CFormer 'cult' leader guilty of
OL,4,Cassaults on nine women
OL,6,FA former priest who ran a "cult-like"
OL,7,Fchurch group has been found guilty of
OL,8,Fa string of indecent assaults against
OL,9,Ffemale followers.
OL,11,FChristopher Brain, 68, from Wilmslow
OL,12,Fin Cheshire, was convicted of attacks
OL,13,Fon nine women as leader of the Nine
OL,14,FO'clock Service (NOS) in Sheffield
OL,15,Fbetween 1986 and 1995.
OL,17,FHe was found guilty by a jury at Inner
OL,18,FLondon Crown Court on Wednesday of 17
OL,19,Fcounts of indecent assault.
