OL,3,CFormer 'cult' leader guilty of
OL,4,Cassaults on nine women
OL,6,FThe jury cleared Brain of a further 15
OL,7,Fcounts of indecent assault and are
OL,8,Fstill deliberating on four counts of
OL,9,Findecent assault and one of rape.
OL,11,FBrian appeared unmoved in the dock as
OL,12,Fthe verdicts were delivered.
OL,14,FProsecutors previously told jurors
OL,15,Fthat the church group - part of the
OL,16,FChurch of England - was aimed at
OL,17,Fyounger people and "presented itself
OL,18,Fto the outside world as a progressive
OL,19,Fforce for good".
