OL,6,FHowever, they also said it had become
OL,7,Fa "cult" in which Brain abused his
OL,8,Fposition to exert control over the
OL,9,Flives of his female followers and
OL,10,Fostracise them from friends and family.
OL,12,FThe court previously heard a "homebase
OL,13,Fteam" was set up to "care for" Brain `
OL,14,Freferred to as "the Lycra Lovelies" or
OL,15,F"the Lycra Nuns."
OL,17,FWitnesses reported seeing the
OL,18,Fdefendant surrounded by women in
OL,19,Flingerie at his home, looking after
OL,20,Fhis needs.
