OL,3,CFormer 'cult' leader guilty of
OL,4,Cassaults on nine women
OL,6,FProsecutor Tim Clark KC said his
OL,7,Fvictims told police Brain groomed them
OL,8,Fand would touch them during massages.
OL,10,FBrain told jurors that some massages,
OL,11,Fintended to be for "tensions" on his
OL,12,Fbody, could evolve into "sensual
OL,13,Ftouching", which he said was between
OL,14,Ffriends and "no big deal".
OL,16,FHe denied touching anyone sexually
OL,17,Fwhile involved with NOS but admitted
OL,18,Fdoing so after he left, but claimed it
OL,19,Fwas consensual.
