OL,7,Ftried to control people by making them
OL,8,Fwear the same clothes or lose weight
OL,9,For that he discouraged them from
OL,10,Fmaintaining friendships.
OL,12,FJurors will return to court on
OL,13,FThursday to continue deliberations.
OL,15,FThe Diocese of Sheffield said it is
OL,16,F"committed to supporting victims,
OL,17,Fsurvivors and all impacted by the
OL,18,Ftrial of Chris Brain" and has a page
OL,19,Ffor those affected on its website.
